Quote:  Craig ... was  doing eight for importing coke and hammer. <i>ibid.</i> 249 HAMMER (n)

Heroin. Dates from mid 1970s, and coincides with the involvement of the criminal element in the drug trade. Cf. hammer-and -tack rhyming slang on `smack'.
